However, President Obama has opened up some lead way for each state to minimize thefrequency of the testing but he stills want to keep annual testing in place (ASCD.org. n.d.).Furthermore, standardized testing is also focusing on the curriculum that was being taught in theclass that may help the child improve academically (Slavin, 2015). When a child is thinkingabout the test, they believe that it always mean a grade and that is not the case.Overall I believe that the test could be less and also be audio standardize testing. At leastif the test is audio, it can better help students that do not understand some of the thing that theyread. I know that when I am reading, I sometimes do not understand the meaning of the word, soI will look up the word to better get and understanding. I tell my children that the test that youtake in school does not define your intelligence it only is set in place for you to know what areyour weakness and strengths.By knowing that information gives them the opportunity to become great and there is nottest in the world that can say otherwise. Some billionaires has never step a foot into college orgraduated high school. It is all about the determination a drive that you feed into their mindsletting them know that they are great and phenomenal and when they set their heart to do greatthat is when they will become masters at what they do.
